# A2A 消息 Schema — T5 报告写作平台

> 版本：v0.1（2026-04-17 草稿）
> 作用：锁定 Coordinator ↔ 4 个子 Agent 之间的消息格式，前后端 + 王亚洲对接 Clawith CollaborationService 时的唯一契约。

---

## 0. 设计原则

1. **统一信封**：所有 Agent 间消息共用同一外层结构，只有 `payload` 内部按 task_type 变化
2. **可追溯**：每条消息带 `task_id` + `parent_task_id` + `focus_ref`，便于版本管理和 UI 回链
3. **可重试**：消息幂等，`task_id` 是去重 key
4. **错误显式**：失败用 `status: "failed"` + `error{}`，不抛异常字符串
5. **流式可选**：长任务（写作/改写）支持 SSE 增量返回，schema 里用 `stream: true` 标记

---

## 1. 消息外层信封（Envelope）

所有 Agent 间消息共用：

```json
{
  "msg_id": "uuid-v4",
  "task_id": "uuid-v4",
  "parent_task_id": "uuid-v4 | null",
  "from_agent": "coordinator | retriever | writer | rewriter | reviewer",
  "to_agent": "coordinator | retriever | writer | rewriter | reviewer",
  "msg_type": "delegate | consult | notify | result | error",
  "task_type": "retrieve | write | rewrite | review | dispatch",
  "focus_ref": "前端 Focus Item ID，用于回链高亮",
  "report_version": "v1 | v2 | ...",
  "timestamp": "ISO8601",
  "stream": false,
  "payload": { /* 按 task_type 不同 */ }
}
```

**字段说明：**

| 字段 | 必填 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|
| msg_id | ✅ | 消息唯一 ID，幂等去重 |
| task_id | ✅ | 任务 ID，跨多条消息共享（同一任务的请求+响应同 task_id） |
| parent_task_id | | 子任务的父任务 ID（Coordinator 拆任务时用） |
| from_agent / to_agent | ✅ | 5 个 Agent 名字之一 |
| msg_type | ✅ | delegate=派发，consult=咨询不写库，notify=单向通知，result=任务结果，error=失败 |
| task_type | ✅ | 5 种任务类型（dispatch 是 Coordinator 内部） |
| focus_ref | | 前端某个聚焦项 ID（如某段落、某章节），结果回来时高亮 |
| report_version | | 该任务关联的报告版本号 |
| stream | | true 时走 SSE，false 走一次性返回 |

---

## 2. 各 task_type 的 payload

### 2.1 `retrieve` — Coordinator → Retriever

**Request payload：**
```json
{
  "query": "字符串：用户原始问题或章节主题",
  "search_scope": {
    "categories": ["政策法规", "行业报告", "历史报告", "媒体资讯"],
    "doc_ids": ["doc_001", "doc_007"],
    "date_range": ["2024-01-01", "2026-04-17"]
  },
  "top_k": 10,
  "rerank": true,
  "min_relevance": 0.6
}
```

**Response payload（result）：**
```json
{
  "query": "原查询回显",
  "results": [
    {
      "chunk_id": "doc_001_p15_3",
      "content": "检索到的文本片段",
      "source": {
        "doc_id": "doc_001",
        "doc_name": "2025年AI行业报告.pdf",
        "page": 15,
        "paragraph_id": "doc_001_p15_3",
        "category": "行业报告"
      },
      "relevance_score": 0.92,
      "highlight_spans": [[12, 28]]
    }
  ],
  "coverage_assessment": "高 | 中 | 低",
  "missing_topics": ["可能缺失的子主题列表"],
  "total_hits": 47
}
```

---

### 2.2 `write` — Coordinator → Writer

**Request payload：**
```json
{
  "mode": "from_outline | mimic | continue",
  "topic": "报告主题",
  "outline": [
    { "level": 1, "title": "一、行业概览", "guidance": "可选写作提示" },
    { "level": 2, "title": "1.1 市场规模" }
  ],
  "retrieval_results": [ /* 来自 Retriever 的 results 数组 */ ],
  "style_reference": {
    "doc_id": "ref_doc_003",
    "aspects": ["tone", "structure", "citation_style"]
  },
  "constraints": {
    "max_length": 5000,
    "language": "zh-CN",
    "must_cite": true,
    "no_fabrication": true
  }
}
```

**Response payload（result）：**
```json
{
  "report_markdown": "# 标题\n\n根据统计，2025年AI市场规模达到3200亿美元 [ref:doc_001_p15_3]...",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "一、行业概览",
      "content": "...",
      "citations": ["doc_001_p15_3", "doc_007_p3_1"]
    }
  ],
  "citation_index": {
    "doc_001_p15_3": { "used_count": 3, "first_section": "1.1" }
  },
  "stats": {
    "word_count": 4200,
    "citation_count": 18,
    "uncited_paragraphs": 0
  }
}
```

---

### 2.3 `rewrite` — Coordinator → Rewriter

**Request payload：**
```json
{
  "mode": "data_update | perspective_shift | content_expansion | style_conversion",
  "source_doc": {
    "doc_id": "user_uploaded_xxx",
    "markdown": "原稿全文 markdown"
  },
  "instructions": {
    "data_update": {
      "new_data_sources": [ /* Retriever 给的新数据 chunks */ ]
    },
    "perspective_shift": {
      "from": "投资人视角",
      "to": "监管者视角",
      "audience": "政府部门"
    },
    "content_expansion": {
      "expand_sections": ["第二章", "第四章"],
      "new_topics": ["碳中和影响", "出海策略"]
    },
    "style_conversion": {
      "from_style": "正式书面",
      "to_style": "通俗易懂",
      "from_lang": "zh-CN",
      "to_lang": "zh-CN"
    }
  },
  "preserve": {
    "structure": true,
    "headings": true,
    "citations": true
  }
}
```

**Response payload（result）：**
```json
{
  "rewritten_markdown": "改写后全文",
  "diff": {
    "format": "unified",
    "content": "@@ -10,3 +10,3 @@\n-2024年市场规模3000亿\n+2025年市场规模3200亿 [ref:doc_001_p15_3]"
  },
  "changes_summary": {
    "mode": "data_update",
    "added_lines": 12,
    "removed_lines": 8,
    "modified_sections": ["1.2", "2.1"],
    "new_content_marked": true
  },
  "preserved_citations": ["doc_002_p7_2"],
  "new_citations": ["doc_001_p15_3"]
}
```

---

### 2.4 `review` — Coordinator → Reviewer

**Request payload：**
```json
{
  "report_markdown": "待审查的报告全文",
  "knowledge_base_snapshot_id": "kb_v_2026_04_17",
  "checks": [
    "citation_validity",
    "data_accuracy",
    "logic_coherence",
    "no_fabrication",
    "format_compliance",
    "coverage"
  ],
  "severity_threshold": "MEDIUM"
}
```

**Response payload（result）：**
```json
{
  "verdict": "pass | needs_revision | fail",
  "issues": [
    {
      "id": "issue_001",
      "type": "citation_error | data_mismatch | logic_break | fabrication | format | coverage",
      "location": {
        "section": "第3章第2段",
        "line_range": [142, 148],
        "citation_id": "doc_001_p15_3"
      },
      "detail": "引用的 chunk 在知识库中不存在",
      "severity": "HIGH | MEDIUM | LOW",
      "suggested_fix": "建议改引 doc_001_p15_4"
    }
  ],
  "scores": {
    "coverage_score": 0.85,
    "quality_score": 0.78,
    "citation_accuracy": 0.95
  },
  "retry_recommended": true
}
```

---

### 2.5 `dispatch` — Coordinator 内部任务编排

Coordinator 拆解用户请求时产生的内部"任务计划"，不发给其他 Agent，但写入 task tree：

```json
{
  "user_request": "原始用户输入",
  "intent": "generate_report | rewrite_report | search_knowledge",
  "subtasks": [
    {
      "task_id": "...",
      "to_agent": "retriever",
      "task_type": "retrieve",
      "depends_on": [],
      "rationale": "为什么派这个任务"
    },
    {
      "task_id": "...",
      "to_agent": "writer",
      "task_type": "write",
      "depends_on": ["上一个 task_id"]
    }
  ],
  "max_review_rounds": 2
}
```

---

## 3. 错误格式（msg_type=error）

```json
{
  "...envelope...": "...",
  "msg_type": "error",
  "payload": {
    "error_code": "RETRIEVAL_TIMEOUT | LLM_RATE_LIMIT | INVALID_INPUT | KB_UNAVAILABLE | INTERNAL",
    "error_message": "人类可读的错误描述",
    "retryable": true,
    "retry_after_seconds": 30,
    "context": { /* 任意调试上下文 */ }
  }
}
```

---

## 4. 流式响应（stream=true）

Writer / Rewriter 长任务建议走 SSE：

```
event: chunk
data: {"task_id": "...", "delta": "新生成的文本片段", "section": "1.1"}

event: chunk
data: {"task_id": "...", "delta": "...", "section": "1.2"}

event: done
data: {"task_id": "...", "final_payload": { /* 完整 result payload */ }}
```

---

## 5. 审查回环（Reviewer → Coordinator → Writer/Rewriter）

```
1. Coordinator → Writer: write (round=1)
2. Writer → Coordinator: result
3. Coordinator → Reviewer: review
4. Reviewer → Coordinator: result(verdict=needs_revision, issues=[...])
5. Coordinator → Writer: write (round=2, payload.revision_context = issues)
6. ... 最多 max_review_rounds 轮，超过则升级给用户
```

第 5 步的 payload 增加：
```json
{
  "revision_context": {
    "round": 2,
    "previous_report": "上一版全文",
    "review_issues": [ /* Reviewer 返回的 issues 数组 */ ],
    "must_fix_severities": ["HIGH"]
  }
}
```

---

## 6. 给王亚洲的对接清单

| 项 | 谁负责 | 备注 |
|----|--------|------|
| Envelope 字段命名 | 共同确认 | 决定后不再改 |
| RAGFlow 接口 → Retriever payload 映射 | 王亚洲 | 把 RAGFlow API 字段映射到 §2.1 response |
| Clawith CollaborationService 是否原生支持 envelope | 王亚洲 | 不支持的话需要薄适配层 |
| SSE / WebSocket 端点路径 | 王亚洲 | `/api/agents/stream/:task_id` |
| 错误码全集 | 共同确认 | 加在 §3 |
| chunk_id 命名规则 | 共同确认 | `{doc_id}_p{page}_{para_idx}` 是否够用 |

